mapper.select: SELECT entry_ha_temp.dairi_cd, entry_ha_temp.dairi_name, entry_ha_temp.upd_date FROM ( SELECT entry_no, serial, ROW_NUMBER() OVER( PARTITION BY entry_no ORDER BY serial DESC ) AS serialrownum FROM entry_ha_temp WHERE entry_no = #{entryNo} AND ( del_flg IS NULL OR del_flg <> '1' ) ) t1, entry_ha_temp WHERE t1.serialrownum = 1 AND entry_ha_temp.entry_no = t1.entry_no AND entry_ha_temp.serial = t1.serial
SELECT T.* FROM (SELECT ROWNUM AS NO, ENTRY_HA_TEMP.* FROM ENTRY_HA_TEMP WHERE entry_no = #{entryNo} ORDER BY serial DESC) T WHERE T.NO = 1
mapper.update: UPDATE ENTRY_HA_TEMP SET pattern_cd = patternCd, hknj1_katen_cd = substr(#{hiKanji1DairiCd},1,4), hknj1_dairi_cd = #{hiKanji1DairiCd}, hknj1_bnt_wari = #{hiKanji1BntWariFrom}, hknj2_katen_cd = substr(#{hiKanji2DairiCd},1,4), hknj2_dairi_cd = #{hiKanji2DairiCd}, hknj2_bnt_wari = #{hiKanji2BntWariFrom}, mosikomi_bungen = #{disBungen}, upd_date=#{updDate} WHERE 1 = 1 AND to_date(check_date) between to_date(#{checkDateFrom}) and to_date(#{checkDateTo})
mapper.select: SELECT COUNT(ENTRY_NO) FROM FILE_ID WHERE ENTRY_NO = #{entryNo} AND FILE_ID = #{fileId}
